We will continue to process applications with staff working remotely. Our telephone line will be closed, but our staff will continue to respond to emails and live chat messages. Read more. Ontario High School Closures: University Application and Admission Guidelines The universities and the Ontario Universities’ Application Centre (OUAC) are monitoring the Ontario high school labour disruptions and school closures due to COVID-19. Read more. Updates to ORPAS Important Dates The following are updated dates for the Occupational Therapy (OT)/Physical Therapy (PT) programs…Read more.
